    "strategic-snark": "Pointed criticism with constructive undertones",
    "soft-roast": "Gentle, accessible humor with limited bite",
    "deadpan": "Completely straight-faced absurdism",
    "socratic": "Feigned naive questioning to expose contradictions"
  },
